WEBVTT

00:18.670 --> 00:19.760
I am Zhuge Yue,

00:20.390 --> 00:23.300
the Fourth Young Master
of the Zhuge family,
a noble family of Great Yong,

00:23.300 --> 00:26.330
and the Master of Qingshan Manor,
a hereditary position in my family.

00:25.910 --> 00:30.120
[Zhuge Yue, Master of Qingshan Manor,
Great Yong]

00:26.600 --> 00:28.160
I pledge loyalty
to the Emperor of Great Yong

00:28.160 --> 00:29.890
and eliminate his dissidents.

00:30.870 --> 00:31.600
He's Yan Xun,

00:31.840 --> 00:33.780
[Yan Xun, Heir Apparent of Great Yan]

00:32.000 --> 00:33.890
the Heir Apparent of the Duke of Dingbei.

00:33.890 --> 00:35.600
The Yan family guarded Great Yan,

00:35.600 --> 00:37.280
but was feared
by the Emperor of Great Yong.

00:37.280 --> 00:39.080
The entire family was wiped out.

00:39.840 --> 00:41.370
We were once close friends.

00:41.430 --> 00:42.200
But now,

00:42.480 --> 00:43.880
we are bitter enemies.

02:18.360 --> 02:19.160
Young Master!

02:33.240 --> 02:34.750
Yue Qi!

02:46.000 --> 02:46.520
My Lord,

02:46.840 --> 02:47.640
it's Miss Chu.

02:52.310 --> 02:53.120
Zhuge Yue!

02:55.850 --> 02:57.410
[Chu Qiao]

03:02.030 --> 03:02.710
Xing.

03:03.710 --> 03:04.400
Move.

03:07.360 --> 03:08.240
Zhuge Yue,

03:08.870 --> 03:10.200
I am sorry.

03:14.080 --> 03:14.800
Yan Xun!

03:15.400 --> 03:16.630
Kill me first!

03:25.560 --> 03:26.430
Zhuge Yue!

03:32.750 --> 03:33.500
Zhuge Yue!

03:34.079 --> 03:34.840
Zhuge Yue!

03:35.910 --> 03:36.960
Xing...

03:37.150 --> 03:37.840
I'm here.

03:39.430 --> 03:41.240
Run.

03:41.470 --> 03:42.000
No.

03:42.280 --> 03:43.800
If we leave, we leave together.

03:43.800 --> 03:45.730
You've always been protecting me.

03:46.430 --> 03:47.240
Now,

03:48.450 --> 03:49.980
it's my turn to protect you.

03:54.190 --> 03:54.910
Zhuge Yue?

03:55.870 --> 03:56.750
Zhuge Yue?

03:57.800 --> 03:59.860
I will definitely get you out of here.

04:00.310 --> 04:01.280
Xing...

04:02.400 --> 04:03.120
You...

04:04.470 --> 04:06.030
will definitely...

04:06.430 --> 04:08.150
get me out of here.

04:17.160 --> 04:18.040
Zhuge Yue?

04:19.870 --> 04:20.630
Zhuge Yue!

04:21.950 --> 04:22.680
Wake up.

04:23.750 --> 04:25.510
Wake up. You promised me

04:25.720 --> 04:27.380
that we would leave together!

04:27.680 --> 04:28.560
Zhuge Yue!

04:29.120 --> 04:31.480
Don't leave me all alone!

04:31.630 --> 04:32.920
No!

05:04.390 --> 05:05.070
Chu,

05:05.750 --> 05:07.550
actually, I have never changed.

05:08.310 --> 05:10.040
It's just that you never knew

05:10.750 --> 05:12.360
what I truly wanted.

06:11.080 --> 06:12.590
Chu!

06:17.640 --> 06:28.650
[REBIRTH]

07:53.690 --> 07:56.230
[Episode 1]

07:57.240 --> 07:58.070
Great Yong,

07:58.390 --> 07:59.190
Biantang,

07:59.560 --> 08:00.270
and Ximeng

08:00.600 --> 08:02.600
divided the land among themselves.

08:02.990 --> 08:04.190
Biantang is prosperous

08:04.190 --> 08:05.390
and peaceful.

08:06.040 --> 08:09.100
Ximeng is bitterly cold,
and its people are suffering.

08:09.600 --> 08:12.270
Great Yong, with its strict hierarchy

08:12.270 --> 08:15.040
and fierce army, became a dominant power.

08:16.390 --> 08:18.780
Great Yan was originally
a vassal of Great Yong,

08:18.780 --> 08:20.070
but, feared for its achievements,

08:20.070 --> 08:21.800
it fell out with Great Yong

08:22.480 --> 08:25.410
and eventually broke away
to establish its own rule.

08:26.390 --> 08:28.000
The young masters
of Great Yong's noble families

08:28.000 --> 08:30.310
enjoy watching slaves fight beasts

08:30.820 --> 08:32.700
and even hunt slaves for sport.

08:37.110 --> 08:39.510
The orphan Chu Qiao
was a slave in her youth.

08:40.010 --> 08:42.250
She despises Great Yong's slave system

08:42.720 --> 08:44.320
and vows to abolish it
and end the violence.

08:44.320 --> 08:45.000
Keep up!

08:56.910 --> 08:58.240
Stay in Qingshan Manor.

08:59.040 --> 08:59.760
From now on,

09:00.510 --> 09:01.870
your name is Xing.

09:02.670 --> 09:04.390
I recognized her unique talent

09:04.390 --> 09:05.720
and trained her as a spy.

09:18.600 --> 09:19.240
Zhuge Yue,

09:19.670 --> 09:22.330
this Xing in your courtyard
has quite the nerve.

09:22.480 --> 09:23.200
I like her.

09:23.600 --> 09:24.510
She's too bold.

09:24.790 --> 09:26.030
She needs strict discipline.

09:26.030 --> 09:26.960
No need for that.

09:27.000 --> 09:28.060
Just give her to me.

09:28.440 --> 09:29.080
No.

09:29.950 --> 09:31.310
Pick another maid.

09:38.670 --> 09:39.870
I beat you every time.

09:40.120 --> 09:41.720
Why do you never get mad at me?

09:42.030 --> 09:42.960
Because...

09:43.510 --> 09:44.870
you're my only friend.

09:45.790 --> 09:47.920
It's not that Great Yan wants to rebel.

09:47.960 --> 09:50.360
It's that Your Majesty wants it to.

09:51.870 --> 09:52.720
I know

09:52.950 --> 09:54.350
you and Yan Xun are close.

09:54.670 --> 09:56.720
I will grant you a favor

09:57.320 --> 09:58.720
and spare Yan Xun's life.

09:59.120 --> 10:01.030
As for whether he will live or die,

10:01.440 --> 10:02.870
it depends on whether you can

10:02.870 --> 10:05.200
take care of this matter for me.

10:05.510 --> 10:06.840
On Jiuyou Platform,

10:07.270 --> 10:09.080
the Emperor of Great Yong ordered Yan Xun,
the hostage prince,

10:09.080 --> 10:10.960
to identify the severed heads
of his family.

10:10.960 --> 10:13.290
Yan Xun, after witnessing his family burn

10:13.670 --> 10:15.240
and his mother die tragically,

10:15.240 --> 10:17.440
felt as if he were falling into an abyss.

10:18.390 --> 10:20.480
Yan Xun!

10:21.440 --> 10:22.530
Zhuge Yue!

10:23.000 --> 10:24.460
Why are you hiding from me?

10:24.940 --> 10:25.610
Or...

10:28.290 --> 10:30.090
are you guilty about something?

10:34.000 --> 10:36.530
His Majesty
wanted to move against Great Yan.

10:36.670 --> 10:37.910
No one could stop it.

10:39.240 --> 10:39.870
Fine.

10:41.480 --> 10:42.550
From now on,

10:42.750 --> 10:44.680
you are the heir of Qingshan Manor,

10:44.720 --> 10:46.720
a promising subject of Great Yong.

10:46.910 --> 10:47.790
Chu and I—

10:47.840 --> 10:50.360
one is the imprisoned descendant
of a disgraced king,

10:50.360 --> 10:52.000
and the other is the Zhuge family's

10:52.000 --> 10:53.870
most insignificant slave.

10:54.520 --> 10:56.450
You don't need to visit us anymore.

10:58.360 --> 11:00.090
We don't want to see you either.

11:00.600 --> 11:01.150
Yan Xun,

11:02.360 --> 11:04.390
I used to see you as a trusted friend.

11:04.910 --> 11:06.840
That's why I petitioned His Majesty

11:06.840 --> 11:09.240
to remove your name
from the execution list

11:10.080 --> 11:11.390
of the Yan family.

11:11.960 --> 11:12.840
As for Xing,

11:13.360 --> 11:14.760
you should know

11:15.670 --> 11:16.720
that to me,

11:17.910 --> 11:20.970
she has long ceased to be
just a slave in Qingshan Manor.

11:37.080 --> 11:38.080
Chu and you—

11:38.390 --> 11:39.270
and your Qingshan Manor—

11:39.270 --> 11:40.600
have long severed ties!

11:41.960 --> 11:42.750
Zhuge Yue,

11:44.030 --> 11:45.160
from this moment on,

11:46.280 --> 11:47.680
we are no longer friends.

11:48.270 --> 11:49.840
We are strangers.

11:50.720 --> 11:51.920
Yan Xun was convinced

11:52.200 --> 11:54.510
that everything was the doing
of Qingshan Manor

11:54.510 --> 11:56.170
and completely broke with me.

11:57.240 --> 11:58.960
Xing rebuilt the Xiuli Army

11:58.960 --> 11:59.960
and helped Yan Xun

12:00.600 --> 12:02.000
escape back to Great Yan.

12:02.750 --> 12:03.390
Xing,

12:03.870 --> 12:04.870
come back with me.

12:05.200 --> 12:07.120
Yan Xun's rebellion won't succeed.

12:07.120 --> 12:07.910
Zhuge Yue,

12:08.200 --> 12:09.670
you once spared my life,

12:10.240 --> 12:11.700
and I am grateful for that.

12:11.830 --> 12:12.730
But that does not erase

12:12.730 --> 12:14.490
the grievances between us.

12:14.720 --> 12:16.670
You are a noble son, high above all.

12:16.870 --> 12:19.130
You care nothing for the lives of slaves.

12:19.240 --> 12:20.300
But they are human,

12:20.390 --> 12:21.850
the family I care for most!

12:22.390 --> 12:24.080
You shot and injured Yan Xun back then,

12:24.080 --> 12:26.120
preventing our escape from the capital

12:26.120 --> 12:28.250
and causing us years of imprisonment.

12:28.750 --> 12:29.630
You and I

12:30.000 --> 12:31.440
have always been on opposite sides.

12:31.440 --> 12:33.040
That can never be reconciled

12:33.670 --> 12:35.510
and will never change.

12:35.840 --> 12:36.510
Xing,

12:38.080 --> 12:39.940
do you really trust Yan Xun so much

12:40.240 --> 12:42.240
and believe he can give you
everything you want?

12:42.240 --> 12:43.120
I trust him.

12:44.270 --> 12:45.960
The morality,

12:46.440 --> 12:47.030
justice,

12:47.360 --> 12:48.620
and ideals you speak of

12:49.440 --> 12:51.100
are not as simple as you think.

12:51.200 --> 12:52.000
Zhuge Yue,

12:53.150 --> 12:55.080
that's the difference between us.

12:56.240 --> 12:57.510
How about we make a bet?

12:58.870 --> 13:00.870
Let's bet that one day in this world,

13:01.150 --> 13:03.390
good will be rewarded,
evil will be punished,

13:03.390 --> 13:05.520
and everyone will be treated equally.

13:07.510 --> 13:08.320
Yan Xun.

13:09.120 --> 13:10.120
Are you ready?

13:10.750 --> 13:12.150
Once this moment passes,

13:12.630 --> 13:14.830
we will never have a chance to turn back.

13:14.870 --> 13:16.270
After ending all of this,

13:16.550 --> 13:18.080
we will return to Great Yan.

13:18.550 --> 13:19.480
I promised you

13:20.270 --> 13:22.470
that I would restore peace to the world.

13:22.480 --> 13:24.360
Avenge the dead of Great Yan!

13:28.630 --> 13:31.200
They wanted to create
a vast world where everyone

13:31.200 --> 13:33.960
could live freely,
with no distinction between high and low.

13:33.960 --> 13:35.240
But Yan Xun's heart

13:35.240 --> 13:37.640
was already soaked in blood and vengeance.

13:38.240 --> 13:39.870
He used my feelings for Xing

13:40.440 --> 13:42.040
to lure me to the frozen lake.

13:42.720 --> 13:45.250
By the time Xing realized
what was happening,

13:45.480 --> 13:46.510
it was too late.

13:47.120 --> 13:47.840
Yan Xun!

13:48.360 --> 13:49.720
Kill me first!

13:51.480 --> 13:52.270
Zhuge Yue!

13:52.960 --> 13:54.360
I am sorry.

14:14.910 --> 14:15.510
No!

14:18.750 --> 14:20.270
Miss Chu, you're awake?

14:23.520 --> 14:25.450
[Su, A Maid of Great Yan]

14:24.370 --> 14:25.830
And your fever has broken.

14:27.390 --> 14:28.240
Who are you?

14:30.440 --> 14:31.510
And where am I?

14:33.270 --> 14:34.120
Miss Chu,

14:34.960 --> 14:36.960
you still don't remember anything?

14:37.270 --> 14:38.390
Miss Chu?

14:43.720 --> 14:45.200
This war has been raging on and off

14:45.200 --> 14:46.600
for nearly 3 months.

14:47.150 --> 14:49.510
Although Great Yong
has fewer troops than Great Yan,

14:49.510 --> 14:51.200
Great Yan is bitterly cold.

14:51.360 --> 14:52.480
In terms of climate and provisions,

14:52.480 --> 14:54.720
they are better suited
for prolonged warfare than we are.

14:54.720 --> 14:56.360
The Seventh Prince,
Zhao Che, who leads their troops,

14:56.360 --> 14:57.360
is a tough opponent.

14:57.360 --> 14:58.960
If he drags this out,

14:57.400 --> 15:00.840
[General Shiyan, Commander
of Black Eagle Army of Great Yan]

14:59.440 --> 15:01.750
I'm afraid General Huan
and the Black Eagle Army

15:01.750 --> 15:02.680
may not hold out.

15:03.000 --> 15:05.130
Zhao Che is holding back his full force

15:05.320 --> 15:07.440
to wear our army down

15:07.620 --> 15:08.600
and force us to retreat.

15:08.600 --> 15:09.930
If we give up now,

15:08.660 --> 15:12.170
[General Cheng Yuan, Guardian
of the Black Eagle Army of Great Yan]

15:11.080 --> 15:12.810
all our efforts will be in vain.

15:14.870 --> 15:15.670
Your Majesty,

15:16.120 --> 15:18.580
Great Yong has already
lost 5 cities in a row,

15:18.630 --> 15:20.150
and their strategist, Zhuge Yue,

15:20.150 --> 15:21.350
has died in Great Yan.

15:21.670 --> 15:23.000
If we push too hard,

15:23.390 --> 15:25.750
I'm afraid both sides
will suffer heavy losses.

15:25.750 --> 15:26.870
Even if we win,

15:27.150 --> 15:28.240
for Great Yan,

15:28.240 --> 15:29.870
the cost will be tremendous.

15:30.270 --> 15:32.630
Your Majesty, please proceed with caution.

15:32.630 --> 15:33.430
Your Majesty,

15:33.670 --> 15:34.750
Miss Chu is awake.

15:38.300 --> 15:39.360
Chu, you're awake?

15:41.460 --> 15:42.100
Doctor,

15:42.750 --> 15:43.960
check on the Queen.

15:43.960 --> 15:44.550
Yes.

15:50.910 --> 15:53.440
Your Majesty,
have you remembered anything?

15:58.440 --> 16:00.440
Why doesn't she remember anything?

16:00.810 --> 16:03.050
Her Majesty's fever
hasn't completely broken,

16:03.050 --> 16:04.270
and she's still not fully conscious.

16:04.270 --> 16:05.440
It may be temporary,

16:05.750 --> 16:07.950
or it could be due to external injuries.

16:08.190 --> 16:09.190
We won't know

16:09.240 --> 16:11.000
until she's

16:11.000 --> 16:12.200
fully awake.

16:13.870 --> 16:14.750
I remember...

16:16.850 --> 16:17.890
you are a doctor.

16:19.870 --> 16:21.360
As for the rest...

16:27.080 --> 16:28.150
I had a dream.

16:28.960 --> 16:30.910
I dreamed I was in a frozen lake.

16:32.550 --> 16:34.480
I was trapped at the bottom of it,

16:36.200 --> 16:37.260
unable to breathe.

16:45.480 --> 16:47.010
Why has she only woken twice

16:48.000 --> 16:49.240
in 3 months,

16:49.790 --> 16:51.590
and each time she was delirious,

16:51.910 --> 16:53.570
unable to remember anything?

16:53.690 --> 16:54.490
Your Majesty,

16:54.670 --> 16:56.190
please do not worry too much.

16:56.190 --> 16:58.720
After falling into the frozen lake,
Her Majesty had a high fever for several days.

16:58.720 --> 17:00.120
The hypothermia in her body

17:00.120 --> 17:01.630
has not completely dissipated.

17:01.630 --> 17:03.630
The fact that she can now
speak and move freely

17:03.630 --> 17:05.270
is already a great relief.

17:05.480 --> 17:07.480
For now, rest is the most important.

17:07.670 --> 17:10.470
As for when she will regain her memory,

17:11.160 --> 17:12.750
you must be patient.

17:13.400 --> 17:14.950
Your Majesty, you can talk

17:14.980 --> 17:16.680
with Her Majesty about the past.

17:16.680 --> 17:17.310
This

17:17.550 --> 17:19.349
may help her recover her memory.

17:20.109 --> 17:20.970
You're saying…

17:22.030 --> 17:23.109
I am the Queen?

17:34.880 --> 17:35.550
Yes.

17:36.380 --> 17:38.050
You are my betrothed queen.

17:38.350 --> 17:39.960
We were to be married

17:41.110 --> 17:43.170
before you fell into the frozen lake.

17:43.510 --> 17:44.640
Married?

17:52.700 --> 17:54.160
Let me show you something.

18:07.830 --> 18:08.510
Chu,

18:09.240 --> 18:11.700
this is the wedding dress
I prepared for you.

18:15.640 --> 18:17.680
We have faced life and death together

18:17.680 --> 18:19.810
and have long committed to each other.

18:20.110 --> 18:21.110
Three months ago,

18:21.510 --> 18:23.200
if not for the scoundrels from Great Yong

18:23.200 --> 18:24.480
sneaking into our land

18:25.270 --> 18:26.750
and attempting to assassinate us

18:26.750 --> 18:27.810
on our wedding day,

18:28.140 --> 18:30.340
you would already be the rightful Queen

18:30.480 --> 18:32.110
of Great Yan.

18:34.880 --> 18:35.590
Great Yong?

18:36.070 --> 18:36.830
Great Yong.

18:37.270 --> 18:38.550
Chu, do you remember?

18:40.510 --> 18:41.550
When I was young,

18:41.880 --> 18:44.590
I was forced to serve as a hostage prince
in Zhenhuang City of Great Yong.

18:44.590 --> 18:46.120
I met you at Qingshan Manor.

18:47.590 --> 18:49.650
Later, my family suffered disaster,

18:51.900 --> 18:52.660
and it was you

18:54.240 --> 18:56.170
who protected me and kept me alive.

19:02.160 --> 19:03.890
Yan Shicheng, Duke of Dingbei,

19:04.030 --> 19:05.430
amassed troops for personal gain,

19:05.430 --> 19:08.030
defied heaven and earth,
deceived the throne,

19:08.200 --> 19:09.510
and misled the people.

19:09.510 --> 19:12.680
He even secretly mobilized the Yan Army,
inciting rebellions across the land.

19:12.680 --> 19:14.680
His disloyalty is known to all.

19:15.400 --> 19:17.200
Fortunately, His Majesty is wise

19:17.200 --> 19:18.480
and blessed by Heaven.

19:18.920 --> 19:20.680
The rebellion of Great Yan
has been quelled,

19:20.680 --> 19:22.700
and the traitors' clan has been executed.

19:22.700 --> 19:24.730
Considering that Yan Xun
grew up in Zhenhuang City

19:24.730 --> 19:25.950
and was not involved in the rebellion,

19:25.950 --> 19:28.340
he is now ordered to identify
the severed heads of the traitors

19:26.090 --> 19:28.010
[Zhuge Huai from the Zhuge Family
of Great Yong]

19:28.750 --> 19:30.270
to atone for his crimes.

19:44.070 --> 19:46.720
Yan Shicheng—

19:47.440 --> 19:49.740
the hereditary King of Great Yan,

19:50.880 --> 19:52.640
the 24th-generation descendant
of Emperor Peiluo,

19:52.640 --> 19:55.310
with the 576th spirit tablet enshrined
in the Chengguang Ancestral Temple

19:55.310 --> 19:57.480
of Shengjin Palace;

19:57.880 --> 19:59.720
the Grand Marshal
of the Northwest Army of Great Yong;

19:59.720 --> 20:01.550
and the King of Zhenxi of Great Yan!

20:01.550 --> 20:04.010
He was executed
at Huolei Plains in Great Yan

20:04.270 --> 20:05.750
on April 14.

20:09.750 --> 20:11.470
Zhuge Huai, I'll kill you!

20:11.640 --> 20:15.240
Yan Ting, eldest son of Yan Shicheng,
King of Zhenxi of Great Yan,

20:17.110 --> 20:18.440
was executed on April 14

20:18.510 --> 20:21.440
at Xunlie Terrace in Great Yan.

20:21.880 --> 20:23.480
The names have all been read.

20:23.640 --> 20:26.510
Heir Apparent Yan,
please identify the traitors.

20:44.200 --> 20:45.260
Accept the decree.

20:47.680 --> 20:48.500
Yan Xun,

20:48.750 --> 20:50.480
hurry up and accept the decree.

20:51.200 --> 20:52.930
Go up there and look at the heads

20:53.640 --> 20:55.500
of your old man and your brothers.

21:07.510 --> 21:10.840
The traitor's son, Yan Xun,
has defied the imperial decree!

21:10.900 --> 21:11.580
Seize him!

21:14.880 --> 21:17.120
Yan Xun!

21:35.270 --> 21:36.200
No!

21:52.510 --> 21:54.000
Yan Xun, you fool!

21:54.440 --> 21:56.750
Do you want to die?

22:14.520 --> 22:16.120
No need to identify anymore.

22:16.790 --> 22:18.390
Arrest the criminal Yan Xun!

22:20.000 --> 22:20.790
Zhuge Yue!

22:21.920 --> 22:23.550
The order from Zhenhuang City

22:23.550 --> 22:24.790
was for him to identify the bodies.

22:24.790 --> 22:26.480
How can we go through the motions?

22:26.480 --> 22:27.280
By doing this,

22:27.510 --> 22:29.590
aren't you afraid
His Majesty will blame you?

22:29.590 --> 22:31.050
Whether he blames me or not

22:31.550 --> 22:32.880
is none of your concern.

22:32.920 --> 22:34.720
If you insist on protecting him,

22:35.070 --> 22:37.070
you have to see if he appreciates it.

22:37.350 --> 22:37.960
Guards!

22:41.750 --> 22:43.010
You Great Yan bastard!

22:43.510 --> 22:45.510
I want you to watch with your own eyes

22:46.690 --> 22:50.120
as your family and relatives
are burned to ashes!

22:52.350 --> 22:53.200
Yan Xun!

22:53.590 --> 22:55.650
Are you going to identify them or not?

22:57.110 --> 22:57.790
Zhuge Huai!

22:58.070 --> 22:59.420
Zhuge Huai, I will kill you!

22:59.420 --> 23:00.790
I'll kill you!

23:01.820 --> 23:03.020
I will identify them!

23:28.940 --> 23:32.240
[Bai Sheng, Wife of Duke of Dingbei]

23:30.920 --> 23:31.750
Xun.

23:36.270 --> 23:37.200
Mother.

23:45.670 --> 23:46.540
Xun.

23:47.550 --> 23:48.270
Don't cry.

23:50.270 --> 23:51.930
The children of our Yan family

23:52.370 --> 23:54.050
shed blood but no tears.

23:54.720 --> 23:55.440
Mother,

23:56.400 --> 23:57.830
what exactly happened?

23:59.000 --> 24:00.660
Do you believe in your father?

24:00.960 --> 24:01.960
I do.

24:02.590 --> 24:03.720
In this world,

24:04.750 --> 24:05.830
not everything

24:05.830 --> 24:07.480
can be explained clearly.

24:11.410 --> 24:12.650
Was it them?

24:18.350 --> 24:20.160
Did they destroy Great Yan?

24:20.880 --> 24:21.510
Xun.

24:23.540 --> 24:24.430
Stand up.

24:32.960 --> 24:34.490
Let me identify the bodies.

24:34.640 --> 24:35.720
Up there...

24:36.070 --> 24:37.240
are my husband,

24:37.790 --> 24:38.680
my son,

24:39.110 --> 24:40.070
my daughter,

24:41.070 --> 24:42.070
and my kin!

24:43.350 --> 24:44.950
I believe that in this world,

24:45.240 --> 24:47.160
no one is more qualified than I am

24:47.160 --> 24:48.350
to do this!

24:48.720 --> 24:49.960
His Majesty appointed Yan Xun

24:49.960 --> 24:51.640
to identify the traitors.

24:52.070 --> 24:54.030
Do you intend to disobey the decree?

24:54.030 --> 24:54.880
Guards!

24:55.480 --> 24:57.680
Seize the people who defied the decree!

24:58.920 --> 25:00.920
The entire Yan family has perished.

25:01.070 --> 25:03.670
Why is Princess Consort Yan
the only survivor?

25:04.290 --> 25:06.140
His Majesty once issued a decree—

25:06.140 --> 25:08.720
as long as Princess Consort Yan
does not leave Zhenhuang City,

25:08.720 --> 25:10.790
no one is to harm her in the slightest.

25:11.550 --> 25:12.350
Zhuge Huai,

25:13.120 --> 25:14.860
do you intend
to disobey the decree as well?

25:14.860 --> 25:15.310
I...

25:19.160 --> 25:19.830
Stand down.

25:28.650 --> 25:29.370
Mother!

25:50.630 --> 25:52.190
This is my husband,

25:53.720 --> 25:55.880
Yan Shicheng,

25:56.120 --> 25:57.980
the hereditary King of Great Yan!

25:58.480 --> 26:00.160
During the Battle of Baima Pass,

26:00.160 --> 26:02.510
an army of 300,000 Quanrong invaded.

26:02.750 --> 26:05.640
Shicheng led his troops
and departed from Great Yan.

26:05.640 --> 26:08.310
For 7 days and nights, he did not
remove his armor or leave his saddle.

26:08.310 --> 26:11.040
He led the charge
and saved Great Yong from peril.

26:12.310 --> 26:14.510
Your Emperor swore an oath on the spot

26:14.830 --> 26:16.430
that Great Yong and Great Yan

26:16.590 --> 26:19.570
would be ruler and subject for generations,
never to forsake one another.

26:19.570 --> 26:21.010
Most of you

26:22.440 --> 26:23.900
were present at that time.

26:26.200 --> 26:27.550
This is my son.

26:28.400 --> 26:30.110
He was 21 years old.

26:31.110 --> 26:32.550
He joined the army at 13,

26:32.550 --> 26:34.350
started as a lowly foot soldier.

26:34.880 --> 26:35.680
In 8 years,

26:35.790 --> 26:38.240
he repelled the Quanrong invasions
67 times

26:38.240 --> 26:40.570
and achieved countless merits in battle.

26:40.830 --> 26:42.270
On the 14th of April,

26:43.260 --> 26:44.440
at Xunlie Terrace,

26:45.200 --> 26:47.130
he was trampled to death by horses.

26:56.240 --> 26:57.720
This is my daughter!

26:58.240 --> 26:59.400
On the 16th of April,

27:00.400 --> 27:03.200
she rode to save her captured mother.

27:03.960 --> 27:06.030
While passing Weishuihong Lake,

27:07.400 --> 27:09.550
she died amidst the chaos of battle.

27:14.350 --> 27:17.240
They were warriors of Great Yan!

27:18.680 --> 27:19.590
Zhuge Huai,

27:20.680 --> 27:22.080
carry out the execution.

27:22.550 --> 27:24.030
Carry out the execution!

27:35.390 --> 27:36.300
Don't!

27:37.030 --> 27:38.830
Don't!

27:41.620 --> 27:42.970
Yan Xun!

27:48.680 --> 27:49.510
Yan Xun!

27:51.480 --> 27:52.400
Yan Xun!

27:52.690 --> 27:53.210
No!

27:54.050 --> 27:54.620
No!

27:57.170 --> 27:57.850
Yan Xun!

27:57.920 --> 27:59.630
Please spare my son.

28:22.160 --> 28:22.790
Mother!

28:30.480 --> 28:31.110
Mother!

28:32.030 --> 28:32.640
Mother!

28:35.440 --> 28:36.720
Why did you do this?

28:38.310 --> 28:39.590
Father is gone.

28:40.440 --> 28:41.920
Brother is gone too.

28:43.030 --> 28:44.920
All our kin are gone.

28:46.920 --> 28:49.230
Are you leaving me too?

28:53.830 --> 28:55.070
X-Xun.

28:56.480 --> 28:57.550
Promise me.

28:58.660 --> 29:00.450
You must live on.

29:03.000 --> 29:05.200
Even if life is worse than death,

29:06.240 --> 29:08.460
you must live on.

29:21.000 --> 29:21.720
Mother!

30:01.010 --> 30:04.980
♪ The sky is so vast ♪

30:05.010 --> 30:07.490
♪ The dark clouds are gray ♪

30:09.890 --> 30:13.650
♪ The rain is falling ♪

30:13.670 --> 30:17.020
♪ The eagle is flying ♪

30:18.720 --> 30:22.510
♪ In the vast wilderness ♪

30:22.530 --> 30:26.000
♪ The wind blows ♪

30:28.030 --> 30:31.100
♪ I'm fearless of death ♪

30:31.330 --> 30:34.850
♪ And I'll never have regrets ♪

30:37.180 --> 30:44.700
♪ The lonely black eagle ♪

30:46.180 --> 30:49.510
♪ Is flying against the light ♪

30:50.330 --> 30:53.530
♪ Where is my hometown? ♪

30:52.440 --> 30:54.000
Yan Xun! Move!

30:54.070 --> 31:03.020
♪ In the vast world ♪

31:03.050 --> 31:06.460
♪ I have no origin ♪

31:07.110 --> 31:10.700
♪ And no destination ♪

31:11.270 --> 31:19.330
♪ A pair of stubborn wings ♪

31:19.550 --> 31:27.820
♪ Is born to fly ♪

31:33.480 --> 31:36.210
You risked everything
to block that blade for me.

31:37.400 --> 31:38.550
From that moment,

31:38.720 --> 31:40.400
I swore never to fail you.

31:43.350 --> 31:44.110
Chu,

31:44.370 --> 31:46.370
you are my chosen Queen of Great Yan.

31:47.070 --> 31:47.720
Let go!

31:50.880 --> 31:51.440
Chu.

31:52.680 --> 31:54.480
It doesn't matter if you don't remember.

31:54.480 --> 31:56.510
For me, just you waking up

31:56.960 --> 31:57.750
is enough.

31:58.270 --> 32:00.070
I won't force you to remember me

32:00.350 --> 32:01.720
and believe what I say.

32:02.720 --> 32:03.720
I will wait for you

32:05.240 --> 32:06.790
until the day you remember.

32:15.590 --> 32:16.390
Your Majesty.

32:28.030 --> 32:28.720
Drink this,

32:29.640 --> 32:30.900
and you'll get better.

32:38.960 --> 32:39.760
Your Majesty.

32:41.440 --> 32:42.240
Your Majesty.

32:42.790 --> 32:43.920
Zhuge Yue's body

32:44.750 --> 32:45.880
has been retrieved.

32:57.440 --> 32:58.400
Lady Chu,

32:58.880 --> 33:00.710
we are discussing how to dispose of

33:00.710 --> 33:03.440
the corpse of Great Yong's
chief general, Zhuge Yue.

33:03.440 --> 33:05.440
Do you have any advice?

33:06.550 --> 33:08.210
He was a general of Great Yong?

33:08.240 --> 33:08.830
Yes.

33:09.070 --> 33:10.000
A few months ago,

33:10.240 --> 33:12.440
if he hadn't led his men into Great Yan

33:12.820 --> 33:15.280
to ambush you and His Majesty
at Mount Ximin,

33:15.640 --> 33:17.960
you wouldn't have fallen into
the frozen lake.

33:17.960 --> 33:19.000
How did he die?

33:19.480 --> 33:20.540
Together with you,

33:20.680 --> 33:22.210
he fell into the frozen lake

33:22.240 --> 33:23.070
and died.

33:23.640 --> 33:25.240
This man committed countless crimes.

33:25.240 --> 33:27.480
He was once your fiercest rival.

33:27.880 --> 33:29.680
When you were a slave in Great Yong,

33:29.680 --> 33:31.440
he repeatedly tortured

33:31.750 --> 33:32.810
and oppressed you.

33:33.060 --> 33:34.840
Later, he prevented you and His Majesty

33:34.840 --> 33:36.030
from returning to Great Yan

33:36.030 --> 33:37.830
and clashed with you many times.

33:38.000 --> 33:40.350
This Moon-breaking Sword
was his personal possession.

33:40.350 --> 33:42.200
It once crossed swords with you.

33:42.440 --> 33:45.750
Do you recall this sword?

34:01.160 --> 34:02.420
Moon-breaking Sword?

34:02.770 --> 34:05.510
The Zhuge family has abused and killed
female slaves for generations.

34:05.510 --> 34:07.070
Your sisters, Qi and Ba,

34:07.480 --> 34:08.739
and your brother Linxi

34:08.760 --> 34:10.510
all died at Zhuge Yue's hands.

34:10.840 --> 34:12.190
Countless soldiers
and civilians of Great Yan

34:12.190 --> 34:14.590
also perished
under the Moon-breaking Sword.

34:14.590 --> 34:16.440
After you escaped Qingshan Manor,

34:16.440 --> 34:19.100
you and His Majesty vowed
to end slavery and war,

34:19.320 --> 34:20.850
and to defeat your enemies.

34:26.360 --> 34:27.560
Take a look, Lady Chu.

34:27.679 --> 34:29.670
Can you recognize this villain
from Great Yong?

34:29.670 --> 34:30.320
After all,

34:31.070 --> 34:33.000
you were with him for so many years.

34:56.400 --> 34:57.400
Then burn him.

34:57.630 --> 34:58.510
Let this sword

34:58.670 --> 35:00.190
and this corpse

35:00.310 --> 35:02.580
appease the souls of Great Yan's people.

35:03.880 --> 35:05.190
Lady Chu was once at Qingshan Manor,

35:05.190 --> 35:06.630
spending day and night with Zhuge Yue...

35:06.630 --> 35:07.230
Enough.

35:12.440 --> 35:13.440
Three months ago,

35:14.030 --> 35:16.090
during the battle at the frozen lake,

35:16.400 --> 35:17.710
if Chu and I hadn't

35:18.030 --> 35:19.130
joined forces

35:19.230 --> 35:20.490
against the Yong Army,

35:21.000 --> 35:21.960
this Zhuge Yue,

35:22.510 --> 35:23.840
who was so elusive,

35:24.590 --> 35:26.990
would still be Great Yan's greatest enemy.

35:27.280 --> 35:28.070
Remember.

35:28.930 --> 35:31.370
Chu is a hero who protected our country.

35:31.440 --> 35:33.510
She is also the only Queen of Great Yan.

35:33.510 --> 35:35.110
As for this sinner's corpse,

35:35.230 --> 35:36.830
Great Yan wants no part of it.

35:37.280 --> 35:39.880
Send him back
to the Zhuge family of Great Yong.

35:48.320 --> 35:49.380
Protect the Queen!

36:15.760 --> 36:16.440
Chu?

36:17.550 --> 36:18.230
Chu?

36:19.030 --> 36:19.670
Chu!

36:22.400 --> 36:23.110
Chu,

36:24.360 --> 36:25.220
how do you feel?

36:25.710 --> 36:27.310
Have you recalled anything?

36:28.480 --> 36:29.960
I feel like I know you.

36:32.070 --> 36:33.280
But I can't remember.

36:33.840 --> 36:35.840
Why did those people want to kill me?

36:35.840 --> 36:37.230
What is going on?

36:37.670 --> 36:38.400
Chu.

36:39.400 --> 36:40.800
Take the medicine first.

37:08.070 --> 37:08.840
Your hand...

37:16.800 --> 37:17.400
Chu!

37:17.880 --> 37:19.110
Do you remember now?

37:25.960 --> 37:26.920
Your hand...

37:30.590 --> 37:31.920
Why is that when I see it,

37:33.190 --> 37:34.880
I feel so sad?

37:39.650 --> 37:40.380
Chu.

37:41.630 --> 37:43.510
I knew our lives

37:45.150 --> 37:46.680
were inseparable long ago.

37:58.880 --> 38:01.670
[Three months ago, Ximeng]

38:22.000 --> 38:23.150
Don't go any further.

38:23.150 --> 38:25.630
Further ahead is Great Yan's territory.

38:26.070 --> 38:28.600
Not until we pass Mount Ximin
will we enter it.

38:29.590 --> 38:30.280
Here,

38:30.710 --> 38:31.910
we can hunt good game.

38:57.190 --> 38:58.400
I have verified it.

38:58.710 --> 39:01.190
This man is indeed General Zhuge Yue
of Great Yong.

39:01.190 --> 39:02.850
Judging by where he was found,

39:03.200 --> 39:04.990
he was carried by the undercurrents
of Qianzhang Lake

39:04.990 --> 39:06.720
and washed up near Mount Ximin.

39:07.480 --> 39:10.610
He is severely injured
and suffering from hypothermia.

39:11.280 --> 39:13.540
It is a miracle he has survived this long.

39:15.280 --> 39:17.660
[King of Ximeng]

39:28.190 --> 39:29.880
But I fear he won't make it.

39:30.590 --> 39:32.800
A dead man is likely of no use.

39:33.480 --> 39:37.060
[Qiu Lin, Left General of Ximeng]

39:33.880 --> 39:34.440
Go.

39:35.590 --> 39:37.230
Throw him back into Qianzhang Lake.

39:37.230 --> 39:39.440
Did I say to let him die?

39:39.590 --> 39:40.510
May I ask,

39:41.150 --> 39:43.280
what use is a dying man?

39:43.510 --> 39:47.230
Sometimes the dead
are more useful than the living,

39:47.820 --> 39:49.540
especially him.

39:53.150 --> 39:54.880
Feed him Bone-Chilling Grass.

39:56.550 --> 39:57.680
News from Great Yan.

39:58.150 --> 39:58.920
Recently,

39:58.920 --> 40:00.750
they have been searching
for his whereabouts.

40:00.750 --> 40:02.680
They want to see him, dead or alive.

40:04.710 --> 40:07.770
There are plenty of death row prisoners
in the dungeon.

40:31.110 --> 40:31.880
Soldiers!

40:32.280 --> 40:32.940
Formation!

40:34.670 --> 40:36.670
Why wouldn't I want to marry Yan Xun?

40:37.490 --> 40:39.650
Great Yong will retreat soon.

40:39.680 --> 40:41.410
His Majesty will then marry her

40:41.670 --> 40:43.070
as the Queen of Great Yan.

40:43.320 --> 40:45.320
As long as you're willing to
put on this wedding robe

40:45.320 --> 40:46.550
and marry me,

40:47.010 --> 40:48.130
I will let her go.
